gna-4-768x937.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-1259x1536.jpg 1259w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-1678x2048.jpg 1678w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-150x183.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1803px) 100vw, 1803px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201803%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-scaled.jpg 1803w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-728x889.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-768x937.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-1259x1536.jpg 1259w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-1678x2048.jpg 1678w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-150x183.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-4-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis is how I make it! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFirst, I break and boil the lasagna noodles. This is kind of nice because you don’t have to worry if the noodles break! I tend to break them into thirds, boil them, then spread them out on some parchment paper and hit with some olive oil spray so they don’t stick. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sheet pan lasagna\" width=\"1675\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sheet Pan Lasagna Is Perfect For The Holiday Season!\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-scaled.jpg 1675w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-728x956.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-768x1009.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-1169x1536.jpg 1169w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-1559x2048.jpg 1559w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-150x197.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1675px) 100vw, 1675px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201675%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-scaled.jpg 1675w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-728x956.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-768x1009.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-1169x1536.jpg 1169w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-1559x2048.jpg 1559w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-150x197.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNext, I brown some ground beef or ground turkey. Or a mix of both! I use a large pot and anywhere from one-and-a-half to two pounds of meat. Go the two pound route if you like things very meaty. This gets browned with lots of garlic, basil, oregano and is finished with some marinara sauce. I definitely use store-bought sauce here because it’s easiest. Rao’s is my favorite. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI also stir in some fresh spinach! It’s nice to get some greens in when it comes to a dish like this. Because they blend in nicely so it’s an added bonus. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sheet pan lasagna\" width=\"1813\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sheet Pan Lasagna Is Perfect For The Holiday Season!\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-scaled.jpg 1813w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-728x884.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-768x932.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-1266x1536.jpg 1266w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-1688x2048.jpg 1688w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-150x182.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1813px) 100vw, 1813px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201813%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-scaled.jpg 1813w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-728x884.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-768x932.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-1266x1536.jpg 1266w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-1688x2048.jpg 1688w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-150x182.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe cheesy ricotta mixture is my favorite part. Ricotta cheese, parmesan cheese, mozzarella cheese and a touch of pesto. I always have pesto in my freezer for reasons just like this. But if you have a jarred version that you love, that works well too. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNow get this: you’re going to add the noodles to the meat sauce and toss them together. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNext, you’re going to spread the whole thing out on a sheet pan! Yep yep yep. This is also when I add a bunch of chopped roasted red peppers. I like them to shine instead of being mixed directly into the sauce. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-96561\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sheet pan lasagna\" width=\"1680\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sheet Pan Lasagna Is Perfect For The Holiday Season!\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-scaled.jpg 1680w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-728x953.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-768x1006.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-1173x1536.jpg 1173w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-1564x2048.jpg 1564w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-150x196.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201680%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-scaled.jpg 1680w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-728x953.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-768x1006.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-1173x1536.jpg 1173w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-1564x2048.jpg 1564w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-150x196.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-8-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThen, dollop it with your ricotta cheese mixture. And add another big sprinkle of cheese. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFinally, it’s time to bake. About 30 minutes is all you need for this to come together in the oven. And you get some super crispy edges of pasta which are my absolute favorite part. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSprinkle it with fresh basil, parm, maybe some crushed red pepper flakes, and serve! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sheet pan lasagna\" width=\"1723\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sheet Pan Lasagna Is Perfect For The Holiday Season!\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-scaled.jpg 1723w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-728x929.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-768x980.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-1203x1536.jpg 1203w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-1604x2048.jpg 1604w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-150x191.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1723px) 100vw, 1723px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201723%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-scaled.jpg 1723w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-728x929.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-768x980.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-1203x1536.jpg 1203w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-1604x2048.jpg 1604w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-150x191.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-13-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWE LOVE THIS.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt is so good and so easy. Perfect when you don’t feel like making traditional lasagna or you are short on time. It’s also a huge hit with everyone! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sheet pan lasagna\" width=\"1727\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sheet Pan Lasagna Is Perfect For The Holiday Season!\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-scaled.jpg 1727w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-728x927.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-768x978.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-1206x1536.jpg 1206w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-1608x2048.jpg 1608w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-150x191.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1727px) 100vw, 1727px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201727%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-scaled.jpg 1727w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-728x927.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-768x978.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-1206x1536.jpg 1206w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-1608x2048.jpg 1608w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-150x191.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-15-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eSheet Pan Lasagna\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-96580\" data-recipe-id=\"96580\" data-servings=\"8\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-17-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSheet Pan Lasagna\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"96580\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 10\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e45\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e35\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003cspan\u003e hour\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e  \u003cspan\u003e20\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis sheet pan lasagna is a perfect holiday meal! It\u0026#39;s easy to make, feeds a crowd and tastes incredible. It also makes a wonderful weeknight meal paired with a big greens salad and garlic bread.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"96580\" data-servings=\"8\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epound\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eof lasagna noodles,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003enoodles broken into thirds\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-olive-oil-25-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77600361?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eolive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1.5 to 2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epounds\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eground beef or turkey,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eor a mix\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/spice-world-fresh-whole-garlic-3ct-bag/-/A-14917318?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic cloves\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/gourmet-garden-lightly-dried-basil-0-42oz/-/A-49132048?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edried basil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-oregano-0-8oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77616564?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edried oregano\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e48\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/rao-39-s-homemade-marinara-sauce-premium-quality-all-natural-tomato-sauce-38-pasta-sauce-keto-friendly-38-carb-conscious-24oz/-/A-13349580?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003emarinara sauce,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etwo 24-ounce jars\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e5\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-baby-spinach-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-54555537?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003efresh baby spinach\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ejar roasted red peppers,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003edrained and chopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"10\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/galbani-part-skim-milk-ricotta-cheese-15oz/-/A-15423796?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ericotta cheese\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"11\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/shredded-mozzarella-cheese-8oz-good-gather-8482/-/A-54337119\u0026amp;aflt=plt?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eshredded mozzarella cheese\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"12\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e⅔\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/sartori-sarvecchio-parmesan-cheese-wedge-5-3oz/-/A-47562259?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eparmesan cheese,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eplus more for topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"13\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e⅓\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eprepared basil pesto\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"14\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/gourmet-garden-lightly-dried-basil-0-42oz/-/A-49132048?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped fresh basil,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"96580\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreheat the oven to 350 degrees F.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eBring a pot of salted water to a boil and cook the lasagna noodles according to the directions, until they are al dente. Remove the noodles and spread them on a towel or sheet of parchment paper, giving them a quick spray of olive oil so they don’t stick.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHeat the olive oil in a large stock pot over medium heat. Add the ground beef/turkey with a big pinch of salt and pepper. Cook, browning on all sides, and break the meat apart with a wooden spoon. Once browned, stir in the garlic, basil and oregano.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd the marinara sauce. Stir in the spinach.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd the broken cooked noodles to the meat sauce. Toss until the noodles are coated.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSpread the noodles and sauce out on a standard baking sheet (13x18). Make sure they are in an even layer. Top with the chopped roasted red peppers.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-6\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn a large bowl, stir together the ricotta, 1.5 cups of the mozzarella, the parmesan and the pesto. Add a pinch of salt and pepper. Stir until combined. Sometimes I also add another shake of basil and oregano here too.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-7\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eDollop the ricotta mixture all over the noodles spread on the sheet. Top with the remaining shredded cheese.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-8\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eBake for 30 to 40 minutes, until golden and bubbly.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96580-step-0-9\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eRemove and sprinkle with fresh basil, extra parmesan and crushed red pepper flakes. Serve!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMain Course\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sheet pan lasagna\" width=\"1725\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sheet Pan Lasagna Is Perfect For The Holiday Season!\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-9-scaled.jpg 1725w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-9-728x929.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-9-768x980.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-9-1204x1536.jpg 1204w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sheet-pan-lasagna-9-1605x2048.jpg 1605w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/shee